COULBOURN DISTRICT BUSINESS
REFERENCES,

BENJAMIN CURMBAN, Justice of the Peace in
and for Sixth Election District, Worcester County,
Persons having business in my line wili do well to
give me a call. Business promptly attended to,
Also, Curmean & Co., Dealers and Manufacturers of
all kinds of lumber, Orders solicited and promptly
filed. Yard and mill in Sixth Election District.
P, O. address, Snow Hill.

URIAH F. SHOCKLHY & CO,, Dealers in and
Manufacturers of all kinds of lumber, Lumber on
hand and for sale at all times. Orders solicited and
promptly filled. P. O. address, Snow Hill, Md.

WILLIAM SHOCKLEY, Surveyor, Contractor,
and Builder. Persons having surveying or con-
tracting will do well to give me a call, P. O, ad-
dreu%now Hill, Md.

PETER SYDNEY SHOCKLEY, Carpenter,
Contractor, and Builder. All persons having any-
thiug to do in my line will find me ready to engage,
P. O, address, Snow Hill, Md,

L. C. MILLS & SON, Manufacturers and Dealers
in all kinds of lumber. L. C. Mills, Dealer in
Goods, Groceries, Hats, Caps, Boots, Shoes, and
kinds of merchandise usually kept in a country
store. P, O. Snow Hill, Md.

PURNELL J. McLAIN, Contractor, Carpenter,
and Builder. All work entrusted to my care, will
receive prompt attention. P. O. Snow Hill, Md,

JOHN W. STURGIS, Manufacturer and Dealer
in all kinds of lumber. Orders solicited and
